{"tid":501132,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人唔識同人打好關係？","createTime":"2017-12-16T13:50:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T16:51:09.000Z","uid":158666,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"11229809822e76167a8babc38ab72358e16165ba","tid":501132,"uid":158666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T13:50:55.000Z","msg":"唔知點解對住啲唔識唔熟既人會好拘謹<br />\n唔識得主動同人講野 人哋同自己開玩笑又唔識應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好驚俾人睇穿自己諗咩<br />\n去到工作環境又唔識得同同事打好關係<br />\n覺得自己好悶又負面又假<br />\n所以一直以來得一個真心好朋友<br />\n想改善又唔知點好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n毒撚性格<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1b075cfbfc6388f1258c8df65f6fec1393f07ae","tid":501132,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T13:57:10.000Z","msg":"懶得打"},{"pid":"6cd2ad95e100fdb577d555999685db45c95267c1","tid":501132,"uid":16256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T15:32:13.000Z","msg":"Me2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c6e0466348c3e104caa6f7157b1991d6968b6f","tid":501132,"uid":158666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T15:43:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>懶得打</blockquote><br />\n我都想懶得打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但有時工作需要都冇辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf4508389790e26bdc1bcf4b345098d7a4268542","tid":501132,"uid":158666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T15:43:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Me2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好想改善下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ad2e29ea4b6ac2bd093f6fb2cff34af29c3959b","tid":